  "cocaineMilestone90Description": "Your brain is actively restoring dopamine receptors and neural pathways. You'll likely notice improvements in focus, decision-making, and emotional regulation. Cognitive function is significantly improved.",
  "cocaineMilestone180Title": "Six Months - Cognitive Gains",
  "cocaineMilestone180Description": "Brain imaging studies show increased gray matter volume in the prefrontal cortex at this stage. Your executive function, memory, and impulse control continue to strengthen. You're thinking more clearly.",
  "cocaineMilestone365Title": "One Year - Cardiovascular Health",
