  "cocaineMilestone730Title": "Two Years - Sustained Recovery",
  "cocaineMilestone730Description": "Brain healing continues with sustained improvements in memory, focus, and emotional regulation. Your neural pathways have significantly reorganized, supporting healthier patterns and better overall wellbeing.",
