  "alcoholMilestone1Title": "Sleep Quality Begins to Improve",
  "@alcoholMilestone1Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 1 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone1Description": "Your REM sleep cycles start to normalize within the first day. While alcohol might help you fall asleep initially, it disrupts deep sleep and REM cycles throughout the night, causing fragmented sleep.",
  "@alcoholMilestone1Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 1 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone3Title": "Hydration Levels Restore",
  "@alcoholMilestone3Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 3 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone3Description": "Your kidneys are recovering from alcohol's diuretic effects. Alcohol suppresses antidiuretic hormone, leading to increased urination and dehydration. By day 3, your body's fluid balance is improving significantly.",
  "@alcoholMilestone3Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 3 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone7Title": "Immune System Strengthens",
  "@alcoholMilestone7Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 7 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone7Description": "Your white blood cells are recovering their function. Even a single bout of heavy drinking can impair immune function for up to 24 hours, and chronic drinking significantly weakens your body's ability to fight infections.",
  "@alcoholMilestone7Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 7 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone14Title": "Brain Volume Recovery Begins",
  "@alcoholMilestone14Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 14 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone14Description": "Rapid recovery of brain volume begins within the first two weeks of abstinence. Research shows evidence of brain tissue recovery starting around 14 days, though full cognitive function continues improving over months.",
  "@alcoholMilestone14Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 14 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone30Title": "Blood Pressure Normalizes",
  "@alcoholMilestone30Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 30 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone30Description": "Your cardiovascular system shows significant improvement. Regular alcohol consumption elevates blood pressure, but abstinence for about a month can help bring blood pressure back to healthier levels.",
  "@alcoholMilestone30Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 30 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone60Title": "Liver Function Improves",
  "@alcoholMilestone60Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 60 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone60Description": "Your liver shows measurable improvement in function. This regenerative organ can recover significantly from alcohol-induced damage, with liver enzymes and fat accumulation showing improvement within 2 months of abstinence.",
  "@alcoholMilestone60Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 60 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone90Title": "Cognitive Function Substantially Improves",
  "@alcoholMilestone90Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 90 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone90Description": "Significant cognitive recovery occurs over the first 3 months. Studies show people who maintain abstinence continue to recover cognitive function over several months, with measurable improvements in memory, concentration, and decision-making.",
  "@alcoholMilestone90Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 90 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone180Title": "Brain Volume and Function Continue Recovery",
  "@alcoholMilestone180Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 180 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone180Description": "Six months of sobriety allows for continued neural recovery. Research indicates that brain volume continues to increase and cognitive abilities continue improving significantly during this period of sustained abstinence.",
  "@alcoholMilestone180Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 180 description"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone365Title": "Cancer Risk Reduction May Begin",
  "@alcoholMilestone365Title": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 365 title"
  },
  "alcoholMilestone365Description": "One year of abstinence may begin to reduce cancer risk. While alcohol clearly increases risk for several cancers (liver, breast, colorectal, esophageal), research on risk reduction timeline is still emerging and varies by cancer type.",
  "@alcoholMilestone365Description": {
    "description": "Alcohol milestone day 365 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone1Title": "Carbon Monoxide Clears",
  "@smokingMilestone1Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 1 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone1Description": "Your blood is breathing again! Within 24 hours, carbon monoxide levels drop to normal and oxygen levels increase. Your heart doesn't have to work overtime anymore to pump poisoned blood around your body.",
  "@smokingMilestone1Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 1 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone3Title": "Nicotine Withdrawal Peaks",
  "@smokingMilestone3Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 3 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone3Description": "The nicotine monster is at its angriest, but you're winning the battle! All nicotine has left your system. The worst cravings happen now, but they're also your ticket to freedom on the other side.",
  "@smokingMilestone3Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 3 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone7Title": "Taste & Smell Dramatically Improve",
  "@smokingMilestone7Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 7 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone7Description": "Food is about to become an adventure again! Smoking destroys taste buds and smell receptors. One week in, and you're rediscovering flavors you forgot existed. Prepare for some serious food appreciation!",
  "@smokingMilestone7Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 7 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone14Title": "Circulation & Walking Improve",
  "@smokingMilestone14Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 14 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone14Description": "Your legs are thanking you with every step! Blood circulation improves dramatically, making walking and exercise noticeably easier. Those stairs aren't looking so intimidating anymore, are they?",
  "@smokingMilestone14Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 14 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone30Title": "Lung Function Increases",
  "@smokingMilestone30Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 30 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone30Description": "Your lungs are throwing a comeback party! Cilia have regrown and are sweeping out years of tar and debris. Lung capacity increases significantly, and that smoker's cough is history.",
  "@smokingMilestone30Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 30 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone90Title": "Heart Attack Risk Drops Significantly",
  "@smokingMilestone90Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 90 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone90Description": "Your heart is sending love letters! Three months smoke-free and your cardiovascular risk has already dropped substantially. Your cardiovascular system is healing faster than you might think possible.",
  "@smokingMilestone90Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 90 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone180Title": "Immune System Strengthens",
  "@smokingMilestone180Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 180 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone180Description": "Your immune system just got a superhero upgrade! Six months without smoking and your white blood cells are back to full strength, fighting infections like the champions they were born to be.",
  "@smokingMilestone180Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 180 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone365Title": "Stroke Risk Reduces Significantly",
  "@smokingMilestone365Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 365 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone365Description": "One full year of freedom! Your stroke risk has decreased substantially, and your blood vessels are healing beautifully. You've officially given your brain the gift of better circulation and protection.",
  "@smokingMilestone365Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 365 description"
  },
  "smokingMilestone1825Title": "Cancer Risk Plummets (5 Years)",
  "@smokingMilestone1825Title": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 1825 title"
  },
  "smokingMilestone1825Description": "Five years of victory! Your risk of mouth, throat, esophagus, and bladder cancers has dropped by half. Lung cancer risk has decreased significantly too. Your cells have had time to repair and regenerate.",
  "@smokingMilestone1825Description": {
    "description": "Smoking milestone day 1825 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone1Title": "Nicotine Cravings Peak",
  "@vapingMilestone1Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 1 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone1Description": "Your brain is throwing a nicotine tantrum, but you're already winning! Within 24 hours, nicotine levels drop dramatically. The worst cravings happen now, but they're also the most important to push through.",
  "@vapingMilestone1Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 1 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone3Title": "Breathing Improves",
  "@vapingMilestone3Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 3 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone3Description": "Your lungs are doing a happy dance! Bronchial tubes begin to relax and lung capacity starts improving. That tight chest feeling from vaping is already beginning to ease up.",
  "@vapingMilestone3Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 3 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone7Title": "Taste & Smell Return",
  "@vapingMilestone7Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 7 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone7Description": "Food is about to taste amazing again! Nicotine dampens taste buds and smell receptors. A week in, and your sensory superpowers are making their comeback tour.",
  "@vapingMilestone7Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 7 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone14Title": "Circulation Improves",
  "@vapingMilestone14Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 14 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone14Description": "Your blood is flowing like a champion! Nicotine constricts blood vessels, but two weeks smoke-free and your circulation is dramatically improving. Cold hands and feet, begone!",
  "@vapingMilestone14Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 14 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone30Title": "Lung Function Recovery",
  "@vapingMilestone30Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 30 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone30Description": "Your lungs are practically throwing a celebration parade! Cilia (tiny lung cleaners) have regenerated and lung function has improved significantly. That morning cough is history!",
  "@vapingMilestone30Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 30 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone60Title": "Anxiety Levels Normalize",
  "@vapingMilestone60Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 60 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone60Description": "Plot twist: vaping was making your anxiety problems worse, not better! Two months in and your baseline anxiety levels are significantly lower. Your nervous system is finally chilling out.",
  "@vapingMilestone60Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 60 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone90Title": "Cognitive Function Sharpens",
  "@vapingMilestone90Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 90 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone90Description": "Brain fog has officially left the building! Three months without nicotine and your cognitive function, focus, and memory are significantly improved. It's like upgrading your mental RAM.",
  "@vapingMilestone90Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 90 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone180Title": "Oral Health Recovery",
  "@vapingMilestone180Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 180 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone180Description": "Your mouth is sending thank-you cards! Six months vape-free and gum inflammation decreases, tooth staining fades, and your risk of oral health issues drops substantially.",
  "@vapingMilestone180Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 180 description"
  },
  "vapingMilestone365Title": "Cardiovascular Risk Reduction",
  "@vapingMilestone365Title": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 365 title"
  },
  "vapingMilestone365Description": "Your heart is literally stronger! One full year and your risk of heart disease has dropped significantly. Your cardiovascular system has recovered from nicotine's daily assault course.",
  "@vapingMilestone365Description": {
    "description": "Vaping milestone day 365 description"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone1Title": "Withdrawal Symptoms Begin",
  "@marijuanaMilestone1Title": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 1 title"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone1Description": "Your brain is adjusting to life without THC! Within 24-48 hours, you might experience irritability, anxiety, or sleep difficulties. This is completely normal - your cannabinoid receptors are starting to reset.",
  "@marijuanaMilestone1Description": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 1 description"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone3Title": "Physical Symptoms Peak",
  "@marijuanaMilestone3Title": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 3 title"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone3Description": "You're at the toughest point, but it's all uphill from here! Days 2-6 typically see peak withdrawal symptoms including headaches, sweating, and mood changes. Your body is working hard to rebalance itself.",
  "@marijuanaMilestone3Description": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 3 description"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone7Title": "Sleep Patterns Improve",
  "@marijuanaMilestone7Title": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 7 title"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone7Description": "Sweet dreams are making a comeback! After a week without cannabis, your natural sleep architecture begins to normalize. REM sleep rebounds, leading to more vivid dreams and better rest quality.",
  "@marijuanaMilestone7Description": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 7 description"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone14Title": "Acute Withdrawal Ends",
  "@marijuanaMilestone14Title": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 14 title"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone14Description": "The storm has passed! Most physical withdrawal symptoms significantly decrease after two weeks. Your mood is stabilizing and daily functioning becomes much easier. The hardest part is behind you.",
  "@marijuanaMilestone14Description": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 14 description"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone30Title": "Memory Function Improves",
  "@marijuanaMilestone30Title": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 30 title"
  },
  "marijuanaMilestone30Description": "Your brain fog is clearing! Research shows that verbal learning and memory begin improving significantly after stopping cannabis use. The hippocampus, crucial for memory formation, starts functioning better.",
  "@marijuanaMilestone30Description": {
    "description": "Marijuana milestone day 30 description"
  },
